*************************************************************************************
This repo is archived. Active work continued in fork https://github.com/pliba/kaminpy
*************************************************************************************

This repository contains new implementations -- in Python -- of the 
interpreters described in Samuel Kamin's excellent PLIBA [1] book. 

[1] Samuel Kamin, "Programming Languages, An Interpreter-Based Approach",
      Addison-Wesley, Reading, MA, 1990. ISBN 0-201-06824-9.
      
Kamin's original source code in Pascal, Tim Budd's C++ implementations,
Norvig's lis.py and other relevant resources are in the references/ 
directory.

The Python interpreters are being written by:

- Luciano Ramalho

Contributors:

- Gustavo De Mari (Twitter: @guhdemari): fixed LaTeX of Tim Budd's report
